lead_paragraph: Zach Duke retired the only batter he faced, birthday boy Adam Wainwright turned the page on a disappointing year and the St. Louis Cardinals strengthened their hold on the final NL wild-card spot.

headline.print_headline: Grichuk Gives Cards Lead, Duke Gets Big K in Win vs Brewers
